item.title: TINA SPECIAL: Karis Anderson, Kristina Love, Tsemaye Bob-Egbe, Rhianne Louise McCaulsky, Jenny Fitzpatrick & Chanel Haynes
item.description:
Ahead of Tina: The Tina Turner Musical closing in the West End, in this episode we revisit the conversations we had with Karis Anderson, Kristina Love, Tsemaye Bob-Egbe, Rhianne Louise McCaulsky, Jenny Fitzpatrick and Chanel Haynes who have all played the title role.


Tina received its world premiere in April 2018 in London and subsequently broke all box office records at the Aldwych Theatre... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/67ad0f71505cb2a0a37271f9

item.title: Between the Seasons: Stories from a South African Childhood
item.description: As we gear up for our new season launch on September 18, we’re taking a trip down memory lane with some of our favorite stories from Trevor’s childhood in South Africa. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/LNIsL2kT
